{"type":"message","id":"5931d1fe","parentId":"3502f50c","timestamp":"2026-03-11T11:32:20.500Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating selfie generation**\n\nI’m thinking about whether my selfie attempt failed. A poll might not be necessary since there’s an alert. However, the HEARTBEAT says I must generate a selfie. I might wait before sending it. In the current channel, I wonder if I really need to send a heartbeat unless there’s an issue. If something needs attention, I shouldn’t include “HEARTBEAT_OK” but rather express the alert. I should also check if the selfie generation is still running. Let's look at the logs.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0261b64ebff6edd50169b152c021088191af13b657cec7c879\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpsVLDR-SiUo3FUiPRuzOtFNBNuP7AiLbgUv8X6mIx5F4NIXXydoWxVHj-FJeVOJKLA4bsIxEDd_cvgMO358sXIiAjB-4DWJc_eEcXPftHxvUyiJJ-TMz9w3VSf41EbZ7Nh_nZQzesfgEVqlCimLh1jnL9ncEl-uKyqNH9pEJWUHubyZdYxKE08t44Gt9luyqcRXnn9jtw1QYpK1A7q3X3t9byPHJgdE-ryXWDLbwPmEmx80HZUqED_UwItAiE3KfvdSL2GYkJv4l19O3fI28kpWrLY4za24wJI4zWp-f-8lzXsJbN_YlEci9StMe8QfQDR4i_sNn5nOBYnBf71PBXG2jQ1rVSluVY-SPDVq5HYkNJoLwexEa8ED9-N6i2yYXrauf5W9hf3-wGg9204eCDHfSHUd1HNYMcAncxfjxfDWUI0RJnuVeFiOWjCXL2AVAMjqsXXP03lOSPZGfoTSY1nNLBACD7DUeXL_nmKFZZiIDlLSVSfqewkoXNKKdw0mLkFTQ__SC8tYgBlx9iUV_QoiQPZ5URQHCAx-00ccqjtLrF17ZvLAeYUGL-v7qPqsHrO_bk0KLKPsK0C8O9wvf6IAp7CTpZZsgFxb5NMPZhIH77cL-ybwKLrMZnysfXM-97sw0iGBgeZyiqWs16_7KsLB-h3nX4y-Zj1PYoCPG938w1cwT5UezE8UELhZLIh-T2S-MQGLDAa4Q_YHIIFt1m8v1wpyXioU6bmiEmQRkpUFP9XiOpPyQgHP6y9ZKkShdgWYHEgFfVJPB6Rm--9apdOihs8bVNIpTr6UkgZ4qQfCBKHYNBw_jT7-uSdO71O9qq4zR4CmdMzNN8XdDE-kJkOq4izjzR_CSerg8uBU-a71ct41poEIP7dc-6j-rH4U5xWtWUM8xPz5-6N1MiFBI50s4QKXvjvvsEfqxmjMr1EnOCzdpcC8F5NhXsRbp-6xBXITOf1I6Vgn8fAivxVDloycMSsGiYuQcwp5DlIUk8aBcNtLyJOyq3kbbgYEG9izwLJYFr1R10xbvmMzpM7g0Ga2mltWBG_0zPcD4a2UGzrQBpXSi49kRJt8Bl-5n91rILr63N5sU3bMCvCfXwgXjXep-Bk9HCa_594MF-PyuSVnVmC2fYqJMXCvz9QLQ_RQirF88UOkVqxoMiCY7v0X4xMk5dnl7legVA